// MainContent.js

import React from "react";
import { Box, Heading, Input, FormControl, FormLabel, Stack, Select, InputGroup, InputRightElement } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import "../custom.css";

function MainContent() {
  return (
    <Box className="main-content">
      <Heading as="h2">Search Criteria</Heading>
      <Stack spacing={4}>
        <FormControl id="keywords">
          <FormLabel>Keywords</FormLabel>
          <Input type="text" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl id="owner" w="50%">
          <FormLabel>Owner</FormLabel>
          <Input type="text" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl id="stars" w="25%">
          <FormLabel>Stars</FormLabel>
          <NumberInput defaultValue={0} min={0} max={300} step={1}>
            <NumberInputField />
            <NumberInputStepper>
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={1} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={2} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={3} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={10} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={20} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={30} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={100} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={200} />
              <NumberIncrementStepper step={300} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={1} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={2} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={3} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={10} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={20} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={30} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={100} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={200} />
              <NumberDecrementStepper step={300} />
            </NumberInputStepper>
          </NumberInput>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl id="last-updated" w="25%">
          <FormLabel>Last Updated (Date)</FormLabel>
          <InputGroup>
            <Input type="date" />
            <InputRightElement pointerEvents="none" children={<i className="calendar-icon" />} />
          </InputGroup>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl id="language" w="25%">
          <FormLabel>Language</FormLabel>
          <Select>
            <option value="javascript">JavaScript</option>
            <option value="python">Python</option>
            {/* Add more language options as needed */}
          </Select>
        </FormControl>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default MainContent;
